\begin_layout Standard
Nowadays, time is becoming the most precious resources that every individual
 has.
 The answer to an efficient schedule in our busy life is any mean that provides
 us useful information at the right time.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Moreover, the automatization of all the processes that can be inferred through
 algorithms could ease the pressure of our daily life allowing us to have
 less tense days.
 Travlendar+ answer the needs described above combining a good software
 with a good User Interface.
\end_layout

