\begin_layout Standard
We assume that the user is using the app through a new generation smartphone
 and that it has installed a browser such as Google Chrome or Safari that
 supports HTML5 and Javascript.
 For the correct functioning of the app, the mobile device needs to have
 a GPS system and a regular internet connection available.
